Global Natural Protein Powder Market Insights
Natural Protein Powder Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 14.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Natural Protein Powder Market Overview
The global natural protein powder market was valued at approximately USD 11.5 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 20.4 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5%. This growth is driven by rising consumer demand for natural and plant-based protein sources, the increasing awareness about health and fitness, and the growing trend of clean label products. The demand for natural protein powders has surged due to the health-conscious consumer base seeking alternatives to traditional protein powders with fewer additives and preservatives.

